Articles.Content:
Hello, I have started a new project called LEO. (Laythe Excursion and Observation). This will be one large vessel taking two landers, an orbital Jool probe, Joovian moon probes, and one command vessel. Its sounds like a handful, but I would love to get your opinions and ideas on this project. The development and creation of this project begins today!

Lander: Needs improvement

Orbital Jool probe: Finished

Joovian moon probes: Prototyping. Lander or orbiter?

Command Vessel: Not started

Note: After the project is completed I will post the craft for download.

Part Mods being used.

American Pack

FASA

Maybe Kethane
